snippet.title: Johnny Depp Reveals The Final Message Sent To Him By Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp Reveals The Final Message Sent To Him By Amber Heard
Subscribe To InformOverload: http://bit.ly/2xB5CqA

When Johnny Depp had to file court documents a few years ago, he included some final text messages that he was receiving from Amber Heard. Along with those text messages though are several other documents that Depp filed showing Ambers tumultuous history. Apparently all of her former lovers have also complained about her treating them the same way she treated Johnny.
